<div xml:space="preserve">
<p begin="31090000t" end="61770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle0">有件事我想先说</p>
<p begin="69660000t" end="77200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1">嗯</p>
<p begin="88370000t" end="112160000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle2">你穿那件制服还真好看啊</p>
<p begin="263690000t" end="312960000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle3">将一路走来的「现在」给毁灭的是</p>
<p begin="313200000t" end="353020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle4">视而不见的「过去」</p>
<p begin="353260000t" end="391960000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle5">和所有被舍弃掉的可能性</p>
<p begin="392200000t" end="437460000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle6">既不可逆也无法起死回生</p>
<p begin="437700000t" end="500080000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle7">一切都将陷入深切伤痛的悲哀之中</p>
<p begin="500320000t" end="531480000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle8">但即使如此</p>
<p begin="531720000t" end="592290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle9">就像心脏的鼓动绝不会停下来一样</p>
<p begin="592530000t" end="615960000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle10">接下来我也会和你</p>
<p begin="616200000t" end="671730000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle11">两个人一起跨越难关</p>
<p begin="671970000t" end="710010000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle12">前往我们所期盼的未来</p>
<p begin="710250000t" end="733430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle13">这次一定会背负着你的一切</p>
<p begin="733670000t" end="766500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle14">到达终点给你看的</p>
<p begin="766740000t" end="803870000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle15">连同被托付的愿望</p>
<p begin="804110000t" end="819270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle16">来终结这一切吧</p>
<p begin="819510000t" end="879450000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle17">这次我一定会全部守护好的</p>
<p begin="879700000t" end="938370000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle18">紧握最后的命运吧 Realize</p>
<p begin="1062170000t" end="1076690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle19">谢谢</p>
<p begin="1076930000t" end="1092470000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle20">听到你这样说</p>
<p begin="1092710000t" end="1128760000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle21">特地把你的记忆给重现出来就有价值了呢</p>
<p begin="1132980000t" end="1151520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle22">这里到底是哪里啊</p>
<p begin="1151770000t" end="1179540000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle23">因为拥有挑战资格的你进入了墓所</p>
<p begin="1179780000t" end="1200780000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle24">所以"试炼"就开始了</p>
<p begin="1201020000t" end="1216830000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle25">就只是这样而已哦</p>
<p begin="1217070000t" end="1232220000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle26">你没有听过吗</p>
<p begin="1232460000t" end="1253000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle27">首先, 去面对自己的过去吧</p>
<p begin="1256670000t" end="1280260000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle28">…我慢慢想起来了</p>
<p begin="1280500000t" end="1300030000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle29">你对我做了什么</p>
<p begin="1300270000t" end="1322980000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle30">我完全不记得你了耶</p>
<p begin="1328610000t" end="1352660000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle31">因为比起去相信你的口风紧不紧</p>
<p begin="1352900000t" end="1384470000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle32">直接去干涉记忆更有效率啊</p>
<p begin="1389630000t" end="1419310000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle33">所以, 我通过这个所谓的"试炼"了吗</p>
<p begin="1428680000t" end="1457000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle34">对从头看到尾的我而言</p>
<p begin="1457240000t" end="1486820000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle35">可以说是取得了非常好的结果了吧</p>
<p begin="1487060000t" end="1513950000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle36">从头到尾, 你…</p>
<p begin="1518790000t" end="1551370000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle37">对不起~那边</p>
<p begin="1551610000t" end="1576080000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle38">连我都不自觉地湿了眼眶呢</p>
<p begin="1576320000t" end="1585730000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle39">吵死了</p>
<p begin="1585970000t" end="1595500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle40">不准跟别人说哦</p>
<p begin="1595740000t" end="1604510000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle41">丢脸死了</p>
<p begin="1604750000t" end="1631620000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle42">是说, 这个世界果然是…</p>
<p begin="1631860000t" end="1649100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle43">是啊</p>
<p begin="1649340000t" end="1670060000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle44">这里是根据你的记忆</p>
<p begin="1670300000t" end="1689600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle45">尽量忠实呈现出来的</p>
<p begin="1689840000t" end="1703590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle46">虚构的世界</p>
<p begin="1708040000t" end="1727240000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle47">当然也包含了你的父母</p>
<p begin="1727480000t" end="1747950000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle48">还有所有的一切哦</p>
<p begin="1752110000t" end="1773050000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle49">真的全部都是虚构的吗</p>
<p begin="1773300000t" end="1796680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle50">有几件事连我自己也不知道耶…</p>
<p begin="1796920000t" end="1825460000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle51">你是真的不知道吗</p>
<p begin="1830070000t" end="1862630000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle52">和你心中所想象的<br />父亲的样子不同这点</p>
<p begin="1862880000t" end="1898130000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle53">你真的连一次都没有怀疑过吗</p>
<p begin="1912340000t" end="1941220000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle54">你真的觉得能够隐藏心中</p>
<p begin="1941460000t" end="1969910000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle55">你以为不为人知的部分吗</p>
<p begin="1970150000t" end="1996310000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle56">你能断定自己不曾</p>
<p begin="1996550000t" end="2029190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle57">对虚构的父亲与妄想的母亲寻求</p>
<p begin="2029430000t" end="2058900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle58">被他们知道内心想法而解脱</p>
<p begin="2059150000t" end="2092590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle59">即便如此还是能爱着自己的利己感情吗</p>
<p begin="2098370000t" end="2135240000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle60">这一切都太过理想又太过刚好了</p>
<p begin="2135480000t" end="2156140000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle61">你不这么觉得吗</p>
<p begin="2173960000t" end="2202530000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle62">…少把我父母当笨蛋了, 艾姬多娜</p>
<p begin="2208700000t" end="2218120000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle63">什么</p>
<p begin="2218360000t" end="2242900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle64">我的答案已经全部传达给他们了</p>
<p begin="2243140000t" end="2256360000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle65">不管是我的爸爸还是妈妈</p>
<p begin="2256600000t" end="2270610000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle66">都已经接受了</p>
<p begin="2277330000t" end="2332420000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle67">而且和我说了"加油", "一路顺风"</p>
<p begin="2332670000t" end="2345180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle68">那个声音, 笑容</p>
<p begin="2345420000t" end="2358450000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle69">还有所有的一切</p>
<p begin="2358690000t" end="2381980000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle70">都已经远远超过我所能想象的范围了</p>
<p begin="2387680000t" end="2398140000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle71">我的父母</p>
<p begin="2398380000t" end="2418040000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle72">可不是凭我有限的想象力</p>
<p begin="2418280000t" end="2434370000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle73">就能局限住的人</p>
<p begin="2434610000t" end="2445210000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle74">少小看他们了</p>
<p begin="2459190000t" end="2484030000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle75">我已经把要传达给他们的一切都传达到了</p>
<p begin="2484270000t" end="2499250000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle76">所以你所说的话</p>
<p begin="2499490000t" end="2516060000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle77">是不可能会迷惑我的</p>
<p begin="2549660000t" end="2564230000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle78">真正的意义上</p>
<p begin="2564470000t" end="2579820000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle79">这场"试炼"到这边才结束了</p>
<p begin="2583410000t" end="2609950000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle80">我也很期待你下一关的表现哦</p>
<p begin="2610190000t" end="2626350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle81">下…下一个关卡</p>
<p begin="2626590000t" end="2634730000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle82">什么啊什么啊</p>
<p begin="2634970000t" end="2650430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle83">试炼不是只有一关而已吗</p>
<p begin="2650670000t" end="2672510000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle84">墓所的"试炼"总共有3个</p>
<p begin="2672760000t" end="2702060000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle85">要从"圣域"中解放出去的话<br />就必须全部通过</p>
<p begin="2706360000t" end="2724080000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle86">终于可以和你说这些了</p>
<p begin="2724320000t" end="2740620000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle87">我很高兴哦</p>
<p begin="2740860000t" end="2761320000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle88">看到你这么惊讶</p>
<p begin="2761560000t" end="2773600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle89">我还满愉快的哦</p>
<p begin="2784610000t" end="2806690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle90">也差不多开始消失了</p>
<p begin="2810590000t" end="2822340000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle91">出去以后</p>
<p begin="2822580000t" end="2848000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle92">你应该就会回到原本的墓所吧</p>
<p begin="2856590000t" end="2872080000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle93">那个, 艾姬多娜</p>
<p begin="2872320000t" end="2880720000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle94">怎么了</p>
<p begin="2880960000t" end="2898560000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle95">难不成是要打我一拳吗</p>
<p begin="2903240000t" end="2933950000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle96">确实, 你有那点程度的权利</p>
<p begin="2937150000t" end="2959060000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle97">不过人家可是女生哦, 脸的话有点…</p>
<p begin="2959310000t" end="2968310000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle98">谢谢你啊</p>
<p begin="2984870000t" end="3009790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle99">就算他们不是真实的</p>
<p begin="3010030000t" end="3040020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle100">就算我其实没有和他们传达到我的想法</p>
<p begin="3040260000t" end="3070230000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle101">但是能够让我有机会把想说的说出来<br />都是多亏了你</p>
<p begin="3074020000t" end="3102290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle102">所以说, 谢谢啦</p>
<p begin="3119630000t" end="3145710000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle103">你这个人还真是难以理解</p>
<p begin="3145950000t" end="3164100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle104">我对你有兴趣到</p>
<p begin="3164340000t" end="3180540000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle105">令人害怕的程度呢</p>
<p begin="3180780000t" end="3209660000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle106">能让魔女大人觉得害怕还真是光荣啊</p>
<p begin="3270510000t" end="3280230000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle107">对了</p>
<p begin="3280470000t" end="3296420000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle108">虽然感觉你好像很期待</p>
<p begin="3296660000t" end="3331480000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle109">我会再继续挑战之后的"试炼"</p>
<p begin="3336740000t" end="3357550000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle110">不过看来是无法达成你的期待了</p>
<p begin="3364500000t" end="3375850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle111">你的意思是</p>
<p begin="3382810000t" end="3397610000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle112">通过"试炼"</p>
<p begin="3397860000t" end="3413290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle113">并将大家从"圣域"解放出去</p>
<p begin="3413530000t" end="3429140000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle114">并不是我的工作</p>
<p begin="3429390000t" end="3439430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle115">你的期待</p>
<p begin="3439680000t" end="3455430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle116">会有别的人来达成的</p>
<p begin="3479180000t" end="3505630000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle117">到底如何呢</p>
<p begin="3613120000t" end="3624140000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle118">这里是</p>
<p begin="3634930000t" end="3663330000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle119">对了, 我接受了"试炼"</p>
<p begin="3700740000t" end="3713370000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle120">爱蜜莉雅</p>
<p begin="3781790000t" end="3793050000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle121">爱蜜莉雅</p>
<p begin="3793290000t" end="3808500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle122">振作一点</p>
<p begin="3808740000t" end="3830380000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle123">爱蜜莉雅, 爱蜜莉雅</p>
<p begin="3842410000t" end="3855100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle124">昴?</p>
<p begin="3866650000t" end="3879630000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle125">对…了</p>
<p begin="3879870000t" end="3908350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle126">我接受了"试验"</p>
<p begin="3914600000t" end="3924970000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle127">然后…</p>
<p begin="3976060000t" end="3986720000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle128">爱蜜莉雅</p>
<p begin="4000150000t" end="4026090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle129">不…不是我</p>
<p begin="4038040000t" end="4047340000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle130">不是的</p>
<p begin="4051170000t" end="4058810000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle131">可是</p>
<p begin="4059050000t" end="4082170000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle132">我就说不是了…</p>
<p begin="4082420000t" end="4098400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle133">等等, 冷静一点</p>
<p begin="4098640000t" end="4115140000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle134">看着我, 爱蜜莉雅</p>
<p begin="4122570000t" end="4130090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle135">不要</p>
<p begin="4130330000t" end="4147140000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle136">不要用那种眼神看我</p>
<p begin="4147380000t" end="4161460000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle137">不要, 不要啊</p>
<p begin="4161700000t" end="4183620000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle138">-不是的…不要…<br />-没事, 没事的</p>
<p begin="4183860000t" end="4193500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle139">我在你身边</p>
<p begin="4193740000t" end="4204490000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle140">我在这里哦</p>
<p begin="4204730000t" end="4219810000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle141">不会让你一个人的</p>
<p begin="4220050000t" end="4231780000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle142">没事的</p>
<p begin="4246230000t" end="4275870000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle143">爸爸, 救我</p>
<p begin="4279230000t" end="4307320000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle144">帕克, 帕克</p>
<p begin="4349900000t" end="4365710000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle145">终于冷静下来了</p>
<p begin="4365950000t" end="4389760000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle146">今天就让她好好休息吧</p>
<p begin="4395780000t" end="4409990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle147">因为香料的催眠作用</p>
<p begin="4410230000t" end="4425610000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle148">应该是不会再做恶梦了</p>
<p begin="4431780000t" end="4454660000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle149">抱歉啊, 让你操心了</p>
<p begin="4454900000t" end="4471870000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle150">这可不是为了巴鲁斯</p>
<p begin="4472110000t" end="4479440000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle151">但这样看来</p>
<p begin="4479680000t" end="4505710000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle152">似乎离从圣域解放出去的目标<br />越来越远了啊</p>
<p begin="4513750000t" end="4534250000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle153">那个, 我可以说句话吗</p>
<p begin="4543000000t" end="4554300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle154">怎么了吗, 奥托</p>
<p begin="4554540000t" end="4584600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle155">说不定有办法在不通过试炼的情形下</p>
<p begin="4584840000t" end="4608660000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle156">也能带大家离开结界的方法</p>
<p begin="4615150000t" end="4627650000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle157">你这家伙在说什么啊</p>
<p begin="4627890000t" end="4642420000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle158">才没有那种方法咧</p>
<p begin="4642660000t" end="4658590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle159">总之先听听看吧</p>
<p begin="4658830000t" end="4672250000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle160">我们现在知道的是混血的人们</p>
<p begin="4672490000t" end="4700530000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle161">碰到结界的时候就会昏过去</p>
<p begin="4700770000t" end="4718290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle162">我也亲眼见到过了</p>
<p begin="4727740000t" end="4737210000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle163">那么</p>
<p begin="4749320000t" end="4771610000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle164">如果把昏倒的人</p>
<p begin="4771860000t" end="4801750000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle165">交给不会被结界影响的人们</p>
<p begin="4802000000t" end="4821070000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle166">搬出去不就好了吗</p>
<p begin="4833570000t" end="4852630000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle167">原来如此, 用这个方法的话</p>
<p begin="4852880000t" end="4865440000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle168">说不定真的可以把大家带出去…</p>
<p begin="4865690000t" end="4881460000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle169">虽然是满愉快的提案</p>
<p begin="4881710000t" end="4900000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle170">不过还是建议你们不要尝试比较好哦</p>
<p begin="4906250000t" end="4953280000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle171">我可不想变成没有灵魂的空壳啊</p>
<p begin="5002480000t" end="5023170000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle172">你是, 那个时候的…</p>
<p begin="5023420000t" end="5037510000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle173">好烫好烫好烫好烫</p>
<p begin="5037760000t" end="5046940000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle174">巴鲁斯, 喝茶</p>
<p begin="5047180000t" end="5056160000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle175">茶你个头啦</p>
<p begin="5056410000t" end="5063340000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle176">烫死了</p>
<p begin="5063590000t" end="5072970000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle177">我脸颊都要烧起来了</p>
<p begin="5073210000t" end="5084980000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle178">还以为是发生什么事了呢</p>
<p begin="5085220000t" end="5093150000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle179">太夸张了吧</p>
<p begin="5093390000t" end="5111260000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle180">明明是男生也太不像样了吧</p>
<p begin="5120240000t" end="5142300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle181">别说些多余的话…</p>
<p begin="5149560000t" end="5173940000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle182">拉姆, 也给我一点茶吧</p>
<p begin="5174180000t" end="5189530000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle183">就只是粗茶而已哦</p>
<p begin="5189770000t" end="5216910000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle184">一般来说不是应该会说的更婉转一点吗</p>
<p begin="5217150000t" end="5232800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle185">只是捡来的树叶泡的而已</p>
<p begin="5237630000t" end="5254520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle186">不过既然是拉姆泡的</p>
<p begin="5254760000t" end="5269270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle187">就给我满怀感恩的喝光吧</p>
<p begin="5287080000t" end="5328590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle188">听说加小鬼又带了外面的人进来</p>
<p begin="5332730000t" end="5352170000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle189">看来是个吵闹的小少爷啊</p>
<p begin="5356260000t" end="5384670000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle190">那个, 你是…</p>
<p begin="5384910000t" end="5406480000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle191">老朽是琉兹·毕尔玛</p>
<p begin="5406720000t" end="5444550000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle192">姑且算是这个村落的代表</p>
<p begin="5444790000t" end="5470430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle193">如各位所见, 已经是个老太太了</p>
<p begin="5470670000t" end="5485430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle194">如我们所见…</p>
<p begin="5492620000t" end="5508120000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle195">也就是说萝莉老婆婆吗</p>
<p begin="5508360000t" end="5524770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle196">虽然总觉得有一天会出现的</p>
<p begin="5525010000t" end="5540810000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle197">不过这也太套路了吧</p>
<p begin="5541050000t" end="5569420000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle198">竟然第一次见面就叫人老婆婆啊…</p>
<p begin="5576530000t" end="5587900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle199">算了</p>
<p begin="5592820000t" end="5611040000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle200">你叫做巴鲁斯</p>
<p begin="5611280000t" end="5632260000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle201">也就是, 斯小鬼对吧</p>
<p begin="5632500000t" end="5647530000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle202">斯小鬼…</p>
<p begin="5647770000t" end="5660780000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle203">所以, 琉兹小姐</p>
<p begin="5661020000t" end="5690590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle204">你刚刚说我那么好的提案不可行<br />的根据是什么呢</p>
<p begin="5690830000t" end="5710260000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle205">还有灵魂的空壳是指?</p>
<p begin="5710500000t" end="5727140000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle206">正如字面的意思</p>
<p begin="5734950000t" end="5767110000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle207">混血的人们会被结界夺走意识</p>
<p begin="5767350000t" end="5777940000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle208">正确来说</p>
<p begin="5778180000t" end="5798130000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle209">是灵魂会被分离出来</p>
<p begin="5801340000t" end="5820980000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle210">灵魂会被分离出来?</p>
<p begin="5825820000t" end="5835100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle211">那个…</p>
<p begin="5835340000t" end="5847810000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle212">也就说</p>
<p begin="5848050000t" end="5876670000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle213">如果混血的人打算勉强通过结界的话</p>
<p begin="5876910000t" end="5898230000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle214">肉体会和灵魂分离</p>
<p begin="5898470000t" end="5928780000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle215">然后就会变成只有灵魂留在结界里面</p>
<p begin="5929020000t" end="5947800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle216">而肉体变成空壳的窘境</p>
<p begin="5948040000t" end="5959040000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle217">这样理解对吗</p>
<p begin="5968650000t" end="5988160000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle218">理解得还满快的嘛</p>
<p begin="5992690000t" end="6011910000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle219">简单来说就是如此</p>
<p begin="6012150000t" end="6055300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle220">单独把没有灵魂的肉体给带到结界之外</p>
<p begin="6055540000t" end="6077740000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle221">也就代表着死亡</p>
<p begin="6081570000t" end="6091750000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle222">死…</p>
<p begin="6111190000t" end="6131960000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle223">茶难喝死了</p>
<p begin="6132200000t" end="6145220000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle224">都是草的味道</p>
<p begin="6151390000t" end="6176910000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle225">是说, 本来就真的是用草泡的啊</p>
<p begin="6186520000t" end="6212190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle226">但是如果说挑战"圣域"的资格</p>
<p begin="6212430000t" end="6228110000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle227">是混血的话</p>
<p begin="6228360000t" end="6243140000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle228">不就代表只要有心的话</p>
<p begin="6243390000t" end="6269470000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle229">琉兹或加菲尔都可以挑战吗</p>
<p begin="6274550000t" end="6287320000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle230">如果只是挑战的话</p>
<p begin="6287560000t" end="6307950000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle231">确实理论上是可能的</p>
<p begin="6308190000t" end="6337300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle232">不过, 要解放"圣域"是不可能的</p>
<p begin="6337540000t" end="6365390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle233">那就是代代相传下来的</p>
<p begin="6365630000t" end="6397040000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle234">和我们"圣域"的居民的契约</p>
<p begin="6481180000t" end="6491330000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle235">昴</p>
<p begin="6499380000t" end="6515560000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle236">早安, 爱蜜莉雅酱</p>
<p begin="6520010000t" end="6530380000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle237">睡得好吗</p>
<p begin="6537100000t" end="6548720000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle238">早安</p>
<p begin="6554730000t" end="6577250000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle239">你一直都陪在我身边吗</p>
<p begin="6577490000t" end="6603810000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle240">反正回房间也睡不着啦</p>
<p begin="6606240000t" end="6632480000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle241">奥托那家伙的梦话吵死了</p>
<p begin="6641700000t" end="6658300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle242">昨天真是对不起</p>
<p begin="6663700000t" end="6692880000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle243">我在墓所的时候超混乱的…</p>
<p begin="6711390000t" end="6726370000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle244">没事没事</p>
<p begin="6726610000t" end="6737180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle245">比起那个…</p>
<p begin="6800290000t" end="6818300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle246">不是, 不是的</p>
<p begin="6818540000t" end="6837070000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle247">咦, 真奇怪啊</p>
<p begin="6837320000t" end="6848820000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle248">为什么我会做这种事…</p>
<p begin="6849060000t" end="6867500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle249">爱蜜莉雅酱终于在无意识下</p>
<p begin="6867740000t" end="6882090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle250">开始会积极的寻求我了吗…</p>
<p begin="6882340000t" end="6887820000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle251">没有哦</p>
<p begin="6888060000t" end="6901520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle252">完全没这回事哦</p>
<p begin="6901760000t" end="6916420000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle253">大概是不小心没注意到吧</p>
<p begin="6916660000t" end="6926850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle254">否定也太快了</p>
<p begin="6927090000t" end="6942470000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle255">还有不小心是怎么回事</p>
<p begin="6942710000t" end="6954570000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle256">那是…</p>
<p begin="6969480000t" end="6989370000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle257">还能笑出来的话应该就没事了</p>
<p begin="6993670000t" end="7025970000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle258">试炼的话今晚再去挑战一次就好了</p>
<p begin="7057460000t" end="7079940000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle259">今晚再一次…</p>
<p begin="7122750000t" end="7141480000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle260">我有话要和巴鲁斯说</p>
<p begin="7154530000t" end="7171220000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle261">关于从"圣域"解放的这件事</p>
<p begin="7171540000t" end="7203900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle262">并不是所有居民都赞成的</p>
<p begin="7209370000t" end="7222800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle263">那是什么意思…</p>
<p begin="7226350000t" end="7241370000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle264">"圣域"的解放</p>
<p begin="7241610000t" end="7285360000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle265">只是琉兹大人以及加菲等强权派在主导</p>
<p begin="7289030000t" end="7326030000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle266">也有不期望从"圣域"解放的保守派在</p>
<p begin="7330870000t" end="7357830000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle267">不期望从"圣域"解放出去…</p>
<p begin="7358070000t" end="7372330000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle268">对保守派来说</p>
<p begin="7372570000t" end="7407450000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle269">跟外面的交流维持在最低限度的现在<br />就是最理想的了</p>
<p begin="7411820000t" end="7430900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle270">如果要刻意破坏的话</p>
<p begin="7431140000t" end="7459060000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle271">对他们来说只是徒增困扰而已</p>
<p begin="7464060000t" end="7478970000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle272">所以姑且不论加菲尔</p>
<p begin="7479210000t" end="7499650000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle273">琉兹也不可以相信的意思吗</p>
<p begin="7499890000t" end="7515310000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle274">还有法兰黛莉卡哦</p>
<p begin="7574840000t" end="7594200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle275">叫爱蜜莉雅大人带着辉石的</p>
<p begin="7594450000t" end="7604910000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle276">可是法兰黛莉卡哦</p>
<p begin="7609710000t" end="7643630000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle277">你是说这些可能都是法兰黛莉卡策划的吗</p>
<p begin="7643870000t" end="7660860000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle278">至少现在的状况和证据都表明</p>
<p begin="7661100000t" end="7690930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle279">法兰黛莉卡一定正在计划着什么</p>
<p begin="7700540000t" end="7730520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle280">事实上爱蜜莉雅也是在千钧一发的险境下</p>
<p begin="7730770000t" end="7740150000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle281">勉强逃出来的</p>
<p begin="7743920000t" end="7756210000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle282">因为巴鲁斯尊贵的…</p>
<p begin="7759410000t" end="7779300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle283">还算的上是尊贵的牺牲的功劳呢</p>
<p begin="7779540000t" end="7792330000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle284">不用刻意修正啦</p>
<p begin="7795730000t" end="7812190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle285">不过, 因为没有真的牺牲掉</p>
<p begin="7812440000t" end="7829020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle286">所以你说的也没错啦</p>
<p begin="7832460000t" end="7847880000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle287">小心一点, 巴鲁斯</p>
<p begin="7851160000t" end="7879750000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle288">对反对解放"圣域"的家伙们来说</p>
<p begin="7880000000t" end="7924980000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle289">最有效的办法就是伤害爱蜜莉雅大人了</p>
<p begin="7928420000t" end="7947360000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle290">现在还不知道敌人到底是谁</p>
<p begin="7954430000t" end="7970720000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle291">务必要随时绷紧神经才行</p>
<p begin="8155460000t" end="8173550000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle292">拉姆也过来嘛</p>
<p begin="8182920000t" end="8203780000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle293">什么嘛真冷淡</p>
<p begin="8204020000t" end="8230140000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle294">你…该不会喜欢拉姆吧</p>
<p begin="8240300000t" end="8255330000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle295">她是个好女人对吧</p>
<p begin="8255570000t" end="8266570000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle296">作为一只雄性</p>
<p begin="8266810000t" end="8303510000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle297">被强大又优秀的雌性给吸引也不奇怪吧</p>
<p begin="8307180000t" end="8329150000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle298">希望这次可以顺顺利利啊</p>
<p begin="8329390000t" end="8357640000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle299">"在大石头上睡觉的话<br />也只能睡一天啊"</p>
<p begin="8357890000t" end="8372180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle300">别再搞笑啦</p>
<p begin="8382730000t" end="8393240000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle301">你啊</p>
<p begin="8393480000t" end="8419260000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle302">出了圣域之后想要去做些什么？</p>
<p begin="8426920000t" end="8441570000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle303">真是突然啊</p>
<p begin="8450080000t" end="8472740000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle304">你问我出去以后要做什么?</p>
<p begin="8472980000t" end="8496660000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle305">像你这种想去哪里就能去的家伙</p>
<p begin="8496900000t" end="8526010000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle306">才不会明白本大爷和老太婆的心情啦</p>
<p begin="8537960000t" end="8557170000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle307">那法兰黛莉卡呢</p>
<p begin="8569270000t" end="8601470000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle308">法兰黛莉卡是怎么<br />看待"圣域"的事情的</p>
<p begin="8601720000t" end="8630690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle309">你这家伙怎么什么都没听说啊</p>
<p begin="8634590000t" end="8651500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle310">那时候只专注在要怎么来而已</p>
<p begin="8651740000t" end="8665910000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle311">没办法问到那么详细啦</p>
<p begin="8668720000t" end="8676940000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle312">你的事情也是</p>
<p begin="8677180000t" end="8693360000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle313">因为有不能说的誓约在</p>
<p begin="8693600000t" end="8709070000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle314">也只听说了名字而已</p>
<p begin="8709310000t" end="8729840000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle315">誓约…誓约的</p>
<p begin="8736640000t" end="8755520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle316">真是方便的借口啊</p>
<p begin="8755760000t" end="8772150000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle317">和饲主一模一样啊</p>
<p begin="8778160000t" end="8807950000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle318">你和法兰黛莉卡感情不好吗</p>
<p begin="8808190000t" end="8830340000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle319">如果是问我们感情好还不好的话</p>
<p begin="8830580000t" end="8842290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle320">才不好啦</p>
<p begin="8846670000t" end="8858540000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle321">比起这种事</p>
<p begin="8858780000t" end="8877470000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle322">你啊, 昨天在墓所…</p>
<p begin="8942200000t" end="8951070000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle323">爱蜜莉雅</p>
<p begin="8982250000t" end="9023810000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle324">对不起…我…我又…</p>
<p begin="9040520000t" end="9052460000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle325">这样啊</p>
<p begin="9052700000t" end="9072950000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle326">真是可惜了</p>
<p begin="9075720000t" end="9113580000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle327">不过, 光是确认试炼的挑战权不会消失</p>
<p begin="9113830000t" end="9126250000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle328">就是一大收获了</p>
<p begin="9133680000t" end="9145340000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle329">所以呢</p>
<p begin="9145580000t" end="9176160000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle330">特地支开爱蜜莉雅是要跟我说什么</p>
<p begin="9176400000t" end="9199830000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle331">只是我的一点小手段罢了</p>
<p begin="9203200000t" end="9234260000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle332">我可没有天真到</p>
<p begin="9234500000t" end="9263800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle333">能让缺乏信用的对象和我同席</p>
<p begin="9264040000t" end="9280310000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle334">缺乏信用?</p>
<p begin="9280550000t" end="9293350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle335">你是说爱蜜莉雅吗</p>
<p begin="9293590000t" end="9305060000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle336">你突然之间在说什么…</p>
<p begin="9305300000t" end="9328100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle337">你冷静点, 昴</p>
<p begin="9332400000t" end="9348050000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle338">我想请你和至今为止一样</p>
<p begin="9348290000t" end="9377720000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle339">帮助并支持爱蜜莉雅大人</p>
<p begin="9377960000t" end="9402170000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle340">那种事不用你说</p>
<p begin="9402410000t" end="9421980000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle341">你要做什么</p>
<p begin="9422220000t" end="9441180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle342">当然是和你一样</p>
<p begin="9441420000t" end="9478690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle343">全力支持爱蜜莉雅大人通过王选</p>
<p begin="9478930000t" end="9487320000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle344">也就是说</p>
<p begin="9487560000t" end="9512060000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle345">我们是共犯呢</p>
<p begin="9512300000t" end="9536520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle346">要说的话也是协力者吧</p>
<p begin="9536760000t" end="9560060000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle347">你说的话充满矛盾</p>
<p begin="9570530000t" end="9586430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle348">怎么说?</p>
<p begin="9591660000t" end="9606620000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle349">别跟我装蒜</p>
<p begin="9606860000t" end="9628370000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle350">爱蜜莉雅参加王选的事情被公开的话</p>
<p begin="9628610000t" end="9642720000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle351">魔女教就会倾巢而出</p>
<p begin="9642960000t" end="9658730000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle352">大家都知道的吧</p>
<p begin="9658970000t" end="9679330000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle353">既然如此你又在干嘛</p>
<p begin="9679570000t" end="9694140000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle354">话说回来你也向爱蜜莉雅</p>
<p begin="9694380000t" end="9718230000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle355">隐瞒了魔女教的情报对吧</p>
<p begin="9718470000t" end="9737820000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle356">爱蜜莉雅什么都不知道</p>
<p begin="9738060000t" end="9762370000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle357">如果知道的话一切应该都会不一样</p>
<p begin="9767680000t" end="9801680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle358">不一样的话, 那些事情…</p>
<p begin="9828000000t" end="9845610000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle359">有你在的话就没事了</p>
<p begin="9850300000t" end="9881500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle360">如果你在的话, 就不会发生那种事了</p>
<p begin="9887360000t" end="9906750000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle361">如果你能保护大家的话…</p>
<p begin="9906990000t" end="9915320000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle362">不过</p>
<p begin="9915560000t" end="9950600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle363">你代替不在场的我, 达到了目的</p>
<p begin="9950840000t" end="9975920000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle364">作为骑士这可是莫大的功劳呢</p>
<p begin="9976160000t" end="9991260000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle365">那种事情</p>
<p begin="9996920000t" end="10010660000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle366">冷静点巴鲁斯</p>
<p begin="10010900000t" end="10031240000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle367">你能接受这种事吗</p>
<p begin="10031480000t" end="10043960000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle368">你也一样, 被留在宅邸</p>
<p begin="10044200000t" end="10068710000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle369">像小石头一样被舍弃了啊</p>
<p begin="10068950000t" end="10082160000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle370">罗兹瓦尔大人所做的事</p>
<p begin="10082400000t" end="10099150000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle371">拉姆都可以接受</p>
<p begin="10102960000t" end="10150130000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle372">不管当下拉姆被怎么摆布或舍弃都一样</p>
<p begin="10163890000t" end="10178370000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle373">那么雷姆</p>
<p begin="10178620000t" end="10214310000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle374">因为那么无聊的理由给牺牲了也能原谅吗</p>
<p begin="10252730000t" end="10279410000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle375">虽然不知道你再说的是谁</p>
<p begin="10279640000t" end="10308260000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle376">不过其他人的名字和拉姆可没关系</p>
<p begin="10345900000t" end="10354050000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle377">为什么</p>
<p begin="10354300000t" end="10378490000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle378">我要将应该告诉爱蜜莉雅大人的情报</p>
<p begin="10378740000t" end="10394920000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle379">给隐藏起来呢</p>
<p begin="10395180000t" end="10430210000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle380">为什么在魔女教袭击而来时</p>
<p begin="10430450000t" end="10455000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle381">我偏偏不在宅邸呢</p>
<p begin="10459760000t" end="10468290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle382">不论哪个问题</p>
<p begin="10468540000t" end="10483210000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle383">答案都是一样的</p>
<p begin="10487980000t" end="10528450000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle384">因为我将所有状况都引导到</p>
<p begin="10534920000t" end="10556840000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle385">不用我来对峙魔女教</p>
<p begin="10557090000t" end="10578760000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle386">就能解决的局面了</p>
<p begin="10579000000t" end="10587440000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle387">什…</p>
<p begin="10605830000t" end="10628160000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle388">如果由我出手解决的话</p>
<p begin="10628400000t" end="10688860000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle389">这次的事情就不会变成<br />爱蜜莉雅大人或是你的功劳了</p>
<p begin="10689100000t" end="10717190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle390">效果非常好对吧</p>
<p begin="10717430000t" end="10742630000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle391">在击退魔女教之前和之后</p>
<p begin="10742870000t" end="10759600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle392">阿拉姆村的居民</p>
<p begin="10759850000t" end="10788350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle393">也对爱蜜莉雅大人的态度<br />180度大转变了</p>
<p begin="10788590000t" end="10812360000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle394">从无法理解的魔女的眷属变成了</p>
<p begin="10812600000t" end="10855250000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle395">为了保护自己的性命而牺牲奉献的恩人…</p>
<p begin="10859320000t" end="10869160000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle396">你…</p>
<p begin="10869400000t" end="10899970000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle397">知道自己现在在说什么吗</p>
<p begin="10900210000t" end="10922150000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle398">那种事只是结果论而已吧</p>
<p begin="10922390000t" end="10933330000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle399">你以为就因为你不在场</p>
<p begin="10933570000t" end="10951090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle400">还有什么都没说的关系</p>
<p begin="10951330000t" end="10967290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle401">死了多少人啊</p>
<p begin="10967540000t" end="11003510000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle402">对同伴的死伤我也表示哀悼</p>
<p begin="11007410000t" end="11033460000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle403">还是说你希望我能对你个人道歉吗</p>
<p begin="11033700000t" end="11040430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle404">不是</p>
<p begin="11040670000t" end="11049070000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle405">不是不是不是</p>
<p begin="11049310000t" end="11058340000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle406">并不是这样的</p>
<p begin="11058580000t" end="11071180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle407">才不是这样</p>
<p begin="11071420000t" end="11092650000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle408">如果我只是什么都做不到的废物</p>
<p begin="11092900000t" end="11108690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle409">你要怎么办啊</p>
<p begin="11108930000t" end="11127370000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle410">如果变成爱蜜莉雅还有村子里的人们</p>
<p begin="11127610000t" end="11145290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle411">谁都救不了的结果的话…</p>
<p begin="11145530000t" end="11161870000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle412">那是因为</p>
<p begin="11162110000t" end="11177360000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle413">我相信你啊</p>
<p begin="11187440000t" end="11213360000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle414">如果是你的话一定会<br />为爱蜜莉雅大人四处奔走</p>
<p begin="11213600000t" end="11242540000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle415">为了和库尔修大人<br />组成同盟而卯足全力</p>
<p begin="11242780000t" end="11274450000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle416">拼上性命去击退来袭的魔女教徒们</p>
<p begin="11274690000t" end="11297450000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle417">我相信你一定会做到这些的</p>
<p begin="11297690000t" end="11320120000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle418">你又知道我什么了</p>
<p begin="11320360000t" end="11331380000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle419">和你分别的时候</p>
<p begin="11331620000t" end="11352030000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle420">我可是彻头彻尾的废物啊</p>
<p begin="11352270000t" end="11372650000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle421">那个废物会变得稍微像样一点</p>
<p begin="11372900000t" end="11390800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle422">可是因为碰到后来的那些事</p>
<p begin="11391040000t" end="11401860000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle423">而且那些后来发生的事</p>
<p begin="11402110000t" end="11424390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle424">只有留在我自己心中啊</p>
<p begin="11424630000t" end="11434970000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle425">你又相信我什么了</p>
<p begin="11435220000t" end="11471970000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle426">看来今晚的谈话就到此为止了呢</p>
<p begin="11477200000t" end="11507060000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle427">顺带一提这件事可别和爱蜜莉雅大人…</p>
<p begin="11512140000t" end="11529900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle428">不可能说的吧</p>
<p begin="11535840000t" end="11562450000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle429">看来你虽然被愤怒给支配了</p>
<p begin="11562690000t" end="11595080000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle430">内心还是正确的理解了现状呢</p>
<p begin="11595320000t" end="11617240000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle431">那就是为了爱蜜莉雅大人的王选</p>
<p begin="11617490000t" end="11657340000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle432">这时候不该和我或是村民们交恶</p>
<p begin="11674760000t" end="11717200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle433">果然你很适合成为我的"共犯者"呢</p>
<p begin="11744140000t" end="11771320000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle434">抱歉, 我又失败了</p>
<p begin="11777230000t" end="11798000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle435">不用太在意啦</p>
<p begin="11798240000t" end="11826590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle436">而且看上去试炼的挑战权也没有消失</p>
<p begin="11826830000t" end="11836100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle437">接下来就只是</p>
<p begin="11836340000t" end="11854640000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle438">爱蜜莉雅酱的意愿而已了</p>
<p begin="11862380000t" end="11882200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle439">我的, 意愿</p>
<p begin="11888920000t" end="11912070000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle440">你很痛苦这件事一看就知道了</p>
<p begin="11912310000t" end="11921780000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle441">但是我觉得</p>
<p begin="11922020000t" end="11937110000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle442">这个将大家从"圣域"解放出去的工作</p>
<p begin="11937350000t" end="11967180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle443">不是你来完成就没有意义了</p>
<p begin="11985360000t" end="11997090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle444">所以为了大家</p>
<p begin="11997330000t" end="12012160000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle445">你愿意再挑战吗</p>
<p begin="12070120000t" end="12085200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle446">昴这个笨蛋</p>
<p begin="12085450000t" end="12101660000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle447">怎么突然骂人</p>
<p begin="12107910000t" end="12135850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle448">用这么温柔的眼神和声音来问的话</p>
<p begin="12136090000t" end="12157110000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle449">怎么能回答做不到嘛</p>
<p begin="12157350000t" end="12190090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle450">虽然我头脑并不是特别好</p>
<p begin="12190330000t" end="12218610000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle451">但我还是知道这件事该由我来完成的</p>
<p begin="12227440000t" end="12241390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle452">别太宠我了</p>
<p begin="12241630000t" end="12253660000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle453">相信我吧</p>
<p begin="12258110000t" end="12294990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle454">不过, 现在的我或许没什么说服力吧</p>
<p begin="12295240000t" end="12307790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle455">没这回事</p>
<p begin="12308030000t" end="12325180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle456">我会相信你好好等着的</p>
<p begin="12347910000t" end="12363860000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle457">嗯, 谢谢</p>
<p begin="12368940000t" end="12409500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle458">但是, 可能会对阿拉姆村的人们<br />造成一些困扰</p>
<p begin="12409740000t" end="12431150000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle459">只有这点我内心还是有点过意不去</p>
<p begin="12437710000t" end="12451820000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle460">如果是那件事的话</p>
<p begin="12452060000t" end="12473150000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle461">能交给我处理吗</p>
<p begin="12485730000t" end="12496470000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle462">我知道了</p>
<p begin="12496710000t" end="12512970000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle463">我相信昴</p>
<p begin="12521960000t" end="12545880000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle464">事到如今也不可能怀疑昴了嘛</p>
<p begin="12552760000t" end="12563160000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle465">我相信你</p>
<p begin="12595270000t" end="12607480000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle466">不过话说回来</p>
<p begin="12607720000t" end="12632720000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle467">真亏你能说服加菲尔呢</p>
<p begin="12632960000t" end="12657490000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle468">虽然是花了整整两天呢</p>
<p begin="12657730000t" end="12685850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle469">总算让他理解只要爱蜜莉雅不离开结界</p>
<p begin="12686100000t" end="12728250000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle470">放走阿拉姆村的人们也不会有问题的</p>
<p begin="12728490000t" end="12743280000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle471">从我个人的观点来看</p>
<p begin="12743520000t" end="12793870000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle472">我可不觉得他是那种<br />会好好听别人说话的类型啊</p>
<p begin="12794110000t" end="12810790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle473">你这家伙明明是商人</p>
<p begin="12811030000t" end="12828630000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle474">还真没有看人的眼光啊</p>
<p begin="12871200000t" end="12894250000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle475">还真是老旧的戏法啊</p>
<p begin="12894490000t" end="12920690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle476">这是出发前佩特拉给我的</p>
<p begin="12920930000t" end="12949690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle477">是法兰黛莉卡采用的新女仆</p>
<p begin="12954380000t" end="12988230000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle478">法兰黛莉卡不会对新人颐指气使的</p>
<p begin="12988470000t" end="13014150000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle479">她可没堕落到那种地步</p>
<p begin="13014390000t" end="13035720000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle480">所以一点都不需要担心那孩子</p>
<p begin="13040480000t" end="13064750000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle481">你到底是相信法兰黛莉卡</p>
<p begin="13065000000t" end="13075930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle482">还是不相信</p>
<p begin="13076170000t" end="13086090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle483">到底是哪边啊</p>
<p begin="13086330000t" end="13102200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle484">她的想法我无从知晓</p>
<p begin="13102450000t" end="13143850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle485">不过我并没有怀疑<br />法兰黛莉卡这个人的本质</p>
<p begin="13147900000t" end="13175120000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle486">还有, 罗兹瓦尔大人有信息要给你</p>
<p begin="13192390000t" end="13220580000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle487">如果和法兰黛莉卡应对<br />会感到不安的话</p>
<p begin="13220820000t" end="13239210000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle488">就请去依靠碧翠丝大人吧</p>
<p begin="13243630000t" end="13256480000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle489">然后就这样对她说</p>
<p begin="13263050000t" end="13292860000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle490">"罗兹瓦尔说了叫我问你"</p>
<p begin="13293100000t" end="13303850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle491">提问?</p>
<p begin="13304090000t" end="13321290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle492">详细的部分拉姆也不知道</p>
<p begin="13321540000t" end="13354270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle493">不过罗兹瓦尔大人也说了</p>
<p begin="13354510000t" end="13368740000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle494">只要碧翠丝大人听到这句话</p>
<p begin="13368980000t" end="13387410000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle495">状况就会有所改变的</p>
<p begin="13408650000t" end="13417630000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle496">昴</p>
<p begin="13437710000t" end="13471600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle497">那个, 难不成我打扰你和拉姆说话了吗</p>
<p begin="13471840000t" end="13491740000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle498">没有, 没问题的</p>
<p begin="13491980000t" end="13519810000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle499">也没说什么重要的事</p>
<p begin="13520050000t" end="13538130000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle500">爱蜜莉雅酱的事才是最优先的</p>
<p begin="13538370000t" end="13561260000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle501">虽然我超开心听到你这么说的</p>
<p begin="13561500000t" end="13592260000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle502">不过现在还是把村里的人当作最优先吧</p>
<p begin="13632870000t" end="13665970000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle503">愿你能蒙受精灵的祝福…</p>
<p begin="13708760000t" end="13736360000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle504">连在结界里面都还麻烦你带路</p>
<p begin="13736600000t" end="13746260000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle505">抱歉啊</p>
<p begin="13746500000t" end="13763300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle506">这没什么啦</p>
<p begin="13769550000t" end="13782920000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle507">比起那个啊, 垃圾</p>
<p begin="13791430000t" end="13801430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle508">你这家伙</p>
<p begin="13801670000t" end="13823800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle509">也接受了墓所的试炼对吧</p>
<p begin="13846930000t" end="13863070000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle510">没什么好隐瞒的啦</p>
<p begin="13866660000t" end="13879170000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle511">看就知道了</p>
<p begin="13884020000t" end="13908090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle512">你问这个要做什么</p>
<p begin="13908330000t" end="13925880000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle513">很简单的事</p>
<p begin="13926120000t" end="13942200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle514">只是要叫你代替爱蜜莉雅大人</p>
<p begin="13942440000t" end="13962230000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle515">继续去挑战"试炼"而已</p>
<p begin="13962470000t" end="13974370000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle516">那可不行</p>
<p begin="13974610000t" end="13988450000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle517">如果这样的话前提就不成立了</p>
<p begin="13988690000t" end="14028640000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle518">话说回来真的有去跨越什么过去的必要吗</p>
<p begin="14028880000t" end="14034930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle519">咦</p>
<p begin="14039780000t" end="14073340000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle520">本大爷也看过爱蜜莉雅大人<br />挑战"试炼"的样子了</p>
<p begin="14073590000t" end="14086880000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle521">当然也包含她的失败啦</p>
<p begin="14092980000t" end="14120000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle522">之前不是还弄得乱七八糟逃出来吗</p>
<p begin="14120240000t" end="14135180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle523">真让人看不下去啊</p>
<p begin="14142530000t" end="14185330000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle524">我相信爱蜜莉雅一定会通过"试炼"的</p>
<p begin="14185570000t" end="14198430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle525">所以…</p>
<p begin="14198670000t" end="14217530000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle526">你要对她有所期待是你的自由</p>
<p begin="14217770000t" end="14255590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle527">不过爱蜜莉雅大人真的能<br />跨越过去的自己吗</p>
<p begin="14255830000t" end="14272250000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle528">哭着说好可怕好可怕什么的</p>
<p begin="14272490000t" end="14285770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle529">才是她的真心话不是吗</p>
<p begin="14292010000t" end="14312610000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle530">爱蜜莉雅的, 真心话</p>
<p begin="14351660000t" end="14372320000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle531">爱蜜莉雅其实…</p>
<p begin="14379830000t" end="14395080000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle532">结界在附近了</p>
<p begin="14402890000t" end="14430630000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle533">本大爷也只能陪你到这里了</p>
<p begin="14448350000t" end="14456780000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle534">拿去吧</p>
<p begin="14472010000t" end="14483280000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle535">这是</p>
<p begin="14489920000t" end="14514590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle536">我可没打算说明我这边的状况</p>
<p begin="14518970000t" end="14545000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle537">只是如果你不回去的话</p>
<p begin="14545240000t" end="14563670000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle538">我们也很困扰</p>
<p begin="14567410000t" end="14576640000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle539">有需要的时候</p>
<p begin="14576890000t" end="14589620000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle540">就把那个给法兰黛莉卡看吧</p>
<p begin="14729120000t" end="14740780000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle541">没事的</p>
<p begin="14809830000t" end="14824330000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle542">一个人都没有吗</p>
<p begin="14941580000t" end="14957330000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle543">这是怎么回事</p>
<p begin="15022390000t" end="15045110000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle544">雷姆, 雷姆</p>
<p begin="15150410000t" end="15160250000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle545">雷姆</p>
<p begin="15508010000t" end="15524790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle546">我们约好了的吧</p>
<p begin="15537370000t" end="15554260000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle547">下次见面之前</p>
<p begin="15559220000t" end="15592590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle548">要好好疼爱自己的肠子</p>
<p begin="15669300000t" end="15698500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle549">(踏出的一步)</p>
</div>
